snippet.title: Gameplay - Strange Ocean
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam today:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2847280/?utm_source=YouTube

Jump geysers in the goofiest gravity, speed under sharks on the silliest seas, and shoot down dangerous pirates with ducks! Join the exuberant Captain Marina as you set sail together in Strange Ocean!
